  "title": "Tutor (Entry Level Welcome) [Rocher | 6 days | up to $3800] - LCYL",
  "description": "<h3><strong>Tuition Teacher (Mass Hiring)</strong></h3><p><strong>Working days : 6 days (off on Friday)</strong><br /><strong>Working hours (Mon - Thurs) : 1130am - 730pm </strong><br /><strong>Sat & Sun : 930 - 630pm</strong><br /><strong>Location: Rochor MRT</strong><br /><strong></strong><br /><strong>Salary:</strong><br /><strong>Diploma : 2.4k - 2.8k</strong><br /><strong>Degree: 2.8k - 3k</strong><br /><strong>Local degree: 3.5-3.8k</strong><br /><br /><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Deliver 1 to 1 engaging lessons based on the centre’s syllabus and materials.</li><li>Teach primary / secondary / JC students (level can be adjusted based on your strength).</li><li>Provide feedback and simple progress updates to parents when needed.</li><li>Help prepare students for school exams and major exams.</li><li>Maintain a positive, encouraging and disciplined environment.</li><li>Assist with simple centre operations (e.g. admin, arranging materials) when required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Minimum Diploma or Degree</strong> in any discipline</li><li>Able to teach at least <strong>one subject</strong> confidently: Math / Science / Chemistry / Biology / Economics</li><li>No prior teaching experience required – <strong>training will be provided</strong>.</li></ul><p><br />To expedite the process, interested candidates may send in your resume:</p><p>Whatsapp: +65 8770 5105(Leroy)</p><p>Cheong Yeat Long | R25145358</p><p>The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</p>",
